s|TAG_BIO_LATEST_NEWS|<b>Priyanka Chopra And Rani Mukherjee Get An Award</b> <br> Date: <A ALT="" TITLE="Priyanka Chopra And Rani Mukherjee Get An Award" HREF="http://www.bollywoodmovies.us/news/2011/05_02_2011.html">05/04/2011</A>: <br> At the recently held Dadasaheb Phalke Academy award ceremony, Bollywood veteran Dharmendra was honoured with the Phalke Ratna award for his contribution to the Hindi film industry spanning five decades. <A ALT="" TITLE="Priyanka Chopra" HREF="http://www.bollywoodmovies.us/actress/priyanka_chopra/bollywood_priyanka_chopra.html">Priyanka Chopra</A> was given the Dadasaheb Phalke Award for her performance in <A ALT="" TITLE="Saat Khoon Maaf Movie Review" HREF="http://www.bollywoodmovies.us/movie_reviews/2010/saat_khoon_maaf.html">Saat Khoon Maaf (2010)</A> , while <A ALT="" TITLE="Rani Mukherjee" HREF="http://www.bollywoodmovies.us/actress/rani_mukherjee/bollywood_rani_mukherjee.html">Rani Mukherjee</A> received the Outstanding Performance in the Film award for her lead role in <A ALT="" TITLE="No One Killed Jessica Movie Review" HREF="http://www.bollywoodmovies.us/movie_reviews/2011/no_one_killed_jessica.html">No One Killed Jessica (2011)</A> . <A ALT="" TITLE="Anushka Sharma" HREF="http://www.bollywoodmovies.us/actress/anushka_sharma/bollywood_anushka_sharma.html">Anushka Sharma</A> got the Excellent Performance in the Film award for <A ALT="" TITLE="Band Baaja Baaraat Movie Review" HREF="http://www.bollywoodmovies.us/movie_reviews/2010/band_baaja_baaraat.html">Band Baaja Baaraat (2010)</A> , while her costar and debutant <A ALT="" TITLE="Ranveer Singh" HREF="http://www.bollywoodmovies.us/actor/ranveer_singh/bollywood_ranveer_singh.html">Ranveer Singh</A> won the Best Debut award. <A ALT="" TITLE="Dabangg Movie Review" HREF="http://www.bollywoodmovies.us/movie_reviews/2010/dabangg.html">Dabangg (2010)</A> actress <A ALT="" TITLE="Sonakshi Sinha" HREF="http://www.bollywoodmovies.us/actress/sonakshi_sinha/bollywood_sonakshi_sinha.html">Sonakshi Sinha</A> received the Best Debutant award.<br><hr size="1" width="100%"> <b>Band Baaja Baaraat Jodi Together Again</b> <br> Date: <A ALT="" TITLE="Band Baaja Baaraat Jodi Together Again" HREF="http://www.bollywoodmovies.us/news/2011/02_07_2011.html">02/11/2011</A>: <br> New debuten of 2010, <A ALT="" TITLE="Ranveer Singh" HREF="http://www.bollywoodmovies.us/actor/ranveer_singh/bollywood_ranveer_singh.html">Ranveer Singh</A> who stolen the show at the 2010 Indian film award shows by winning Best Debut awards at all shows. Now Ranveer will again be paired with his Band Baaja Baaraat co star <A ALT="" TITLE="Anushka Sharma" HREF="http://www.bollywoodmovies.us/actress/anushka_sharma/bollywood_anushka_sharma.html">Anushka Sharma</A> in a new movie being proceduced by Aditya Chopra. In the new movie called <A ALT="" TITLE="Ladies vs Rikki Bahl Movie Review" HREF="http://www.bollywoodmovies.us/movie_reviews/2011/ladies_vs_rikki_bahl.html">Ladies vs Rikki Bahl (2011)</A> Ranveer will play Rikki Bahl who is a smooth and charming conman, who cons girls for a living but finally meets his match in Anushka. The movie is set to starts shooting early April with plans to be in theatres worldwide on 9th Dec 2011, the same weekend his first movie was <A ALT="" TITLE="Band Baaja Baaraat Movie Review" HREF="http://www.bollywoodmovies.us/movie_reviews/2010/band_baaja_baaraat.html">Band Baaja Baaraat (2010)</A> released. The movie will also bring together others who were part of Band Baaja Baaraat, to include Lyricist Amitabh Bhattacharya, music director Salim Merchant, Sulaiman Merchant and Habib Faisal.|g
